Name: Lichen Salad
AttributesDescription: Increases Max HP of all Resonators in the team by 25%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: In Lahai-Roi, every edible ingredient is treasured, even the humble Cradle Lichen. A handful of fresh, lightly seasoned lichen mixed with the nuts of Creeping Torchpine creates a simple yet nourishing Royan delicacy rich in dietary fiber.
